# Copy this to .env.local and fill with your Kit credentials.
# Use either KIT_FORM_ID (recommended) or KIT_TAG_ID.
# In production, set these in Vercel Project Settings → Environment Variables.

# Server-side ConvertKit credentials (Settings → Advanced)
# Prefer using KIT_API_SECRET on the server. If you only have an API Key, set KIT_API_KEY instead.
KIT_API_SECRET=qezxjTeUeACE1VTCsMtmE1f8MFyHRDtXEsvi1ckMopw
# KIT_API_KEY=

# Preferred: Form to subscribe users to (Grow → Landing Pages & Forms)
# IMPORTANT: Use the NUMERIC Form ID, NOT the data-uid from the embed code.
#
# To find your Form ID:
# 1. Go to Kit (app.kit.com) → Grow → Landing Pages & Forms
# 2. Click your form
# 3. Look at the embed code for: data-sv-form="12345678" ← use this number
#    OR in the URL: app.kit.com/forms/designers/12345678
#
# Example:
#   ✅ KIT_FORM_ID=8189766
#   ❌ KIT_FORM_ID=152cc23834  (this is data-uid, not the Form ID!)
KIT_FORM_ID=8189766

# Optional: If you don't want to use a Form, you can subscribe to a Tag instead
# Must also be numeric. Find in: Grow → Tags
# KIT_TAG_ID=
